@startuml ReportEase_Sequence_Authentification
!theme plain
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #F4F6F7
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #7F8C8D
skinparam ArrowColor #2C3E50
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #7F8C8D
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FEF9E7
skinparam noteBorderColor #B7950B

title Diagramme de Sequence — S'authentifier (SPA + API REST)

actor       "Utilisateur"        as U
participant "SPA\n(React)"       as SPA
participant "API REST\n(Django)" as API
database    "MongoDB"            as DB

== Connexion ==
U   -> SPA : Saisit email + mot de passe
SPA -> API : POST /auth/login
API -> DB  : Recherche utilisateur
DB  --> API: Donnees utilisateur

alt Identifiants invalides
  API --> SPA: 401 Unauthorized
  SPA --> U  : "Identifiants incorrects"
else Compte non valide
  API --> SPA: 403 Forbidden
  SPA --> U  : "Compte non valide"
else Succes
  API --> SPA: 200 OK + {access, refresh, user}
  SPA -> SPA : Stocke les tokens JWT
  SPA --> U  : Redirection selon le role
end

== Acces aux ressources protegees ==
U   -> SPA : Action sur l'application
SPA -> API : Requete + Header\nAuthorization: Bearer <access>
API -> API : Verifie le JWT
API --> SPA: Donnees demandees

note right of API
  Redirection apres login :
  - doctor   -> /dashboard
  - admin    -> /admin/dashboard
  - adminIT  -> /adminit/dashboard
end note

@enduml
